Detailed Description

Class FemusInit.

Petsc include files.

This class is useful to handle multilevel variables. It's going to be split into meshvariables and solutionvariables

This class contains the fe basis function and their derivatives

◆ compute_norm_of_errors_of_unknowns()

template<class real_num , class real_num_mov >
void femus::compute_norm_of_errors_of_unknowns ( MultiLevelProblem &  ml_prob)

@assignment You need to evaluate your manufactured right hand side at the quadrature point qp. Hence, you need to compute the coordinates of the quadrature point. Let us call them x_qp. These are obtained just like every quantity at a quadrature point, i.e., by interpolating the values of the quantity at the element nodes. The interpolation is performed by using the shape functions. In other words, (x_qp) = summation of (x_nodes) * (shape function of that node, evaluated at qp)

(x_nodes) are obtained from geom_element.get_coords_at_dofs_3d() (this is a vector< vector >, where the outer index is the dimension and the inner index ranges over the nodes) (shape function of that node, evaluated at qp) is obtained from phi_u (this is a vector, whose index ranges over the nodes)

243  dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end());
244 
245  if( assembleMatrix ) s.new_recording();
246 
247  //Moving coordinates (Moving frame)
248  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
249  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
250  vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
251  }
252  }
253 
254  // Boundary integral
255  {
256  double tau = 0.;
257  vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
258 
259  // loop on faces
260  for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
261  std::vector < double > xx(3, 0.);
262 
263  // look for boundary faces
264  if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
265  unsigned int face = -(mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
266 
267  if ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "U", tau, face, 0.) && tau != 0.) {
268 
269  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
270  const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
271 
272  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
273  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
274  unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
275 
276  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
277  vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim])(iDof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
278  }

283

288

291  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
292  }
293  else { //if solid node it goes to DX, DY, DZ
294  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
295  }
296  }
297  }
298  }
299  }
300  }
301  }
302  }

304  // *** Gauss point loop ***
305  double area = 1.;
306  adept::adouble supg_tau;
307 
308  for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
309  // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
310  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, jacobian, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
311  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, jacobian_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
312  phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
313 
314  if (flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
315  if (ig == 0) {
316  double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
317  area = jacobian_hat / GaussWeight;
318 
319  if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
320  area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
321  area_elem_first->close();
322  rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
323  }
324  }
325 
326  jacobianOverArea = jacobian_hat / area * rapresentative_area;
327  }
328 
329  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
330  // displacement and velocity
331  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
332  SolVAR[i] = 0.;
333 
334  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
335  GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
336  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
337  }
338 
339  for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
340  NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
341  NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
342  }
343 
344  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
345  SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
346 
347  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
348  GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
349  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
350  }
351 
352  for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
353  NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
354  NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] += nablaphi_hat[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
355  }
356  }
357  }
358 
359  // pressure
360  SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
361 
362  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
363  adept::adouble soli = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
364  SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * soli;
365  }
366 
367  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
368  //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY
369  if (flag_mat == 2) {
370  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
371  {
372  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
373 
374  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
375  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
376 
377  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
378  for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
379  LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolhatVAR[idim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim]) ;
380  }
381  }
382 
383  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
384  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (!solidmark[i]) * (-LapmapVAR[idim] * jacobianOverArea);
385  }
386 
387  //END redidual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
388 
389  //BEGIN redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
390  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
391  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
392 
393  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
394  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
395  //LapvelVAR[idim] += GradSolVAR[dim+idim][jdim]*gradphi[i*dim+jdim];
396  LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
397  AdvaleVAR[idim] += SolVAR[dim + jdim] * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] * phi[i];
398  }
399  }
400 
401  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
402  adept::adouble value = (-AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
403  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
404  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
405  ) * jacobian;
406 
407  if ((!solidmark[i])) {
408  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value;
409  }
410  else {
411  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value;
412  }
413 
414  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
415  }
416  }
417  }
418  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
419 
420  //BEGIN continuity block
421  {
422  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
423 
424  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
425  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
426  }
427 
428  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
429  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * jacobian;
430  }
431  }
432  //END continuity block
433  }
434  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY
435 
436  //*******************************************************************************************************
437 
438  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY
439  else {
440 
441 
442  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
443  //physical quantity
444  adept::adouble J_hat;
445  adept::adouble I_e;
446  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
447  adept::adouble Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
448 
449  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
450  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
451 
452  if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
453  adept::adouble e[3][3];
454 
455  //computation of the stress tensor
456  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
457  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
458  e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
459  }
460  }
461 
462  I_e = 0;
463 
464  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
465  I_e += e[i][i];
466  }
467 
468  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
469  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
470  //incompressible
471  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2. * (incompressible) * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
472  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
473  }
474  }
475  }
476 
477  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
478  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
479  adept::adouble B[3][3];
480 
481  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
482  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
483  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
484  }
485  }
486 
487  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
488  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
489 
490  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
491  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
492  B[I][J] = 0.;
493 
494  for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
495  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
496  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
497  }
498  }
499  }
500 
501  if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
502  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
503 
504  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
505  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
506  if (1 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * B[I][J]
507  - (incompressible) * mus * I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
508  else if (2 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus / J_hat * B[I][J]
509  - (incompressible) * mus / J_hat * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
510  else if (3 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) / J_hat
511  + lambda / J_hat * log(J_hat) * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
512  else if (4 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - I1_B * Id2th[I][J] / 3.) / pow(J_hat, 5. / 3.)
513  + lambda * (J_hat - 1.) * Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
514 
515  }
516  }
517  }
518  else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
519  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
520  - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
521  + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
522  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
523  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
524 
525  invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2]) * invdetB;
526  invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
527  invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
528  invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
529  invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
530  invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
531  invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
532  invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
533  invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
534 
535  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
536  I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
537  - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
538 
539  double C1 = mus / 3.;
540  double C2 = C1 / 2.;
541 
542  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
543  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
544  Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
545  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
546  - (incompressible) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
547  }
548  }
549 
550  }
551  }
552 
553  //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
554 
555  //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
556  {
557  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
558 
559  //BEGIN redidual v=0 in fixed domain
560  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
561  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += (-phi[i] * (-SolVAR[dim + idim])) * jacobian_hat;
562  }
563 
564  //END redidual v=0 in fixed domain
565 
566  //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
567  adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
568 
569  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
570  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
571  CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
572  }
573  }
574 
575  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
576  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (phi[i] * _gravity[idim] - CauchyDIR[idim]) * jacobian;
577  }
578 
579  //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
580  }
581  }
582  //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
583 
584  //BEGIN continuity block
585  {
586  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
587 
588  if (!penalty) {
589 
590  if (0 == solid_model) {
591  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
592  }
593  else if (1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model) {
594  if (incompressible) aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * (J_hat - 1. + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim]) * jacobian_hat;
595 // else aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += /*phi1[i]*/ /** 1.e10 */ SolVAR[2 * dim];
596  else aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i];
597  }
598  else if (2 == solid_model) {
599  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (log(J_hat) / J_hat + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
600  }
601 
602  }
603  else {
604  if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model) { // pressure = 0 in the solid
605  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * (SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
606  }
607 
608  }
609  }
610  }
611  //END continuity block
612  }
613 
614  //END SOLID ASSEMBLY
615  }
616 
617  //BEGIN local to global assembly
618  //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
619  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
620  Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
621 
622  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
623  Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
624  }
625  }
626 
627  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
628 
629  for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
630  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
631  }
632 
633  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
634  myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
635  }
636 
637  if( assembleMatrix ){
638  //Store equations
639  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
640  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
641  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
642  }
643 
644  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
645  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
646

656  }

766  Jac.reserve(dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1)*dim * max_size * (2 * dim + 1));
767 
768  // ------------------------------------------------------------------------
769  // Physical parameters
770  double rhof = ml_prob.parameters.get < Fluid>("Fluid").get_density();
771  double mu_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid>("Solid").get_lame_shear_modulus();
772  double lambda_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid>("Solid").get_lame_lambda();
773  double mus = mu_lame / rhof;
774  double IRe = ml_prob.parameters.get < Fluid>("Fluid").get_IReynolds_number();
775  double lambda = lambda_lame / rhof;
776  double betans = 1.;
777  int solid_model = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid>("Solid").get_physical_model();
778 
779  bool incompressible = (0.5 == ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid>("Solid").get_poisson_coeff()) ? 1 : 0;
780  const bool penalty = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid>("Solid").get_if_penalty();
781 
782  // gravity
783  double _gravity[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
784 
785  // -----------------------------------------------------------------
786  // space discretization parameters
787  unsigned SolType2 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("U"));
788  unsigned SolType1 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(ml_sol->GetIndex("P"));
789 
790  // mesh and procs
791  unsigned nel = mymsh->GetNumberOfElements();
792  unsigned igrid = mymsh->GetLevel();
793  unsigned iproc = mymsh->processor_id();
794 
795  //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
796  //variable-name handling
797  const char varname[7][3] = {"DX", "DY", "DZ", "U", "V", "W", "P"};
798  vector < unsigned> indexVAR(2 * dim + 1);
799  vector < unsigned> indVAR(2 * dim + 1);
800  vector < unsigned> SolType(2 * dim + 1);
801 
802  for (unsigned ivar = 0; ivar < dim; ivar++) {
803  indVAR[ivar] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
804  indVAR[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
805  SolType[ivar] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar][0]);
806  SolType[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
807  indexVAR[ivar] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar][0]);
808  indexVAR[ivar + dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[ivar + 3][0]);
809  }
810 
811  indexVAR[2 * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex(&varname[6][0]);
812  indVAR[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex(&varname[6][0]);
813  SolType[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType(&varname[6][0]);
814  //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
815 
816  int nprocs = mymsh->n_processors();
817  NumericVector* area_elem_first;
818  area_elem_first = NumericVector::build().release();
819 
820  if (nprocs == 1) {
821  area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, SERIAL);
822  }
823  else {
824  area_elem_first->init(nprocs, 1, false, PARALLEL);
825  }
826 
827  area_elem_first->zero();
828  double rapresentative_area = 1.;
829 
830  start_time = clock();
831 
832  if( assembleMatrix ) myKK->zero();
833 
834  // *** element loop ***
835  for (int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++) {
836 
837  short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType(iel);
838  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType2);
839  unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber(iel, SolType1);
840  int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial(iel);
841 
842  // *******************************************************************************************************
843 
844  //initialization of everything in common between fluid and solid
845 
846  //Rhs
847  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
848  dofsVAR[i].resize(nve);
849  Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
850  aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
851  }
852 
853  dofsVAR[2 * dim].resize(nve1);
854  Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
855  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
856 
857  dofsAll.resize(0);
858 
859  // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
860  // coordinates, solutions, displacement and velocity dofs
861 
862  solidmark.resize(nve);
863 
864  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
865  vx[i].resize(nve);
866  vx_hat[i].resize(nve);
867  }
868 
869  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
870  unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType2);
871 
872  // flag nodes on the fluid-solid interface
873  solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark(iDof);
874 
875  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
876  Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]])(iDof);
877  Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]])(iDof);
878 
879  aRhs[indexVAR[j]][i] = 0.;
880  aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
881 
882  //Fixed coordinates (Reference frame)
883  vx_hat[j][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[j])(iDof);
884  // displacement dofs
885  dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel);
886  // velocity dofs
887  dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel);
888  }
889  }
890 
891  // pressure dofs
892  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
893  unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType[2 * dim]);
894  dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel);
895  Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]])(iDof);
896  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
897  }
898 
899  // compose the system dofs
900  for (int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++) {
901  dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end());
902  }
903 
904  dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end());
905 
906  if( assembleMatrix ) s.new_recording();
907 
908  //Moving coordinates (Moving frame)
909  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
910  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
911  vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
912  }
913  }
914 
915  // Boundary integral
916  {
917  double tau = 0.;
918  vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
919 
920  // loop on faces
921  for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
922  std::vector < double > xx(3, 0.);
923 
924  // look for boundary faces
925  if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
926  unsigned int face = -(mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
927 
928  if ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "U", tau, face, 0.) && tau != 0.) {
929  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
930  const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
931 
932  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
933  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
934  unsigned iDof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
935 
936  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
937  vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim])(iDof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
938  }
939  }
940 
941  for (unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++) {
942  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, jacobian, phi, gradphi, normal);
943 
944  // *** phi_i loop ***
945  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
946  adept::adouble value = -phi[i] * tau / rhof * jacobian;
947  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
948 
949  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
950  if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) { //if fluid node it goes to U, V, W
951  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
952  }
953  else { //if solid node it goes to DX, DY, DZ
954  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += value * normal[idim];
955  }
956  }
957  }
958  }
959  }
960  }
961  }
962  }
963 
964  // *** Gauss point loop ***
965  double area = 1.;
966  adept::adouble supg_tau;
967 
968  for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
969  // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
970  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, jacobian, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
971  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, jacobian_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
972  phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
973 
974  if (flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
975  if (ig == 0) {
976  double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
977  area = jacobian_hat / GaussWeight;
978 
979  if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
980  area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
981  area_elem_first->close();
982  rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
983  }
984  }
985 
986  jacobianOverArea = jacobian_hat / area * rapresentative_area;
987  }
988 
989  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
990  // displacement and velocity
991  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
992  SolVAR[i] = 0.;
993 
994  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
995  GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
996  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
997  }
998 
999  for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
1000  NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1001  NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1002  }
1003 
1004  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
1005  SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1006 
1007  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1008  GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1009  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1010  }
1011 
1012  for (int j = 0; j < 3 * (dim - 1); j++) {
1013  NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1014  NablaSolhatVAR[i][j] += nablaphi_hat[inode * 3 * (dim - 1) + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1015  }
1016  }
1017  }
1018 
1019  // pressure
1020  SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
1021 
1022  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
1023  adept::adouble soli = Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
1024  SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * soli;
1025  }
1026 
1027  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1028  //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY
1029  if (flag_mat == 2) {
1030  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1031  {
1032  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1033 
1034  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
1035  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1036 
1037  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1038  for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1039  LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolhatVAR[idim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim]) ;
1040  }
1041  }
1042 
1043  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1044  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (!solidmark[i]) * (-LapmapVAR[idim] * jacobianOverArea);
1045  }
1046 
1047  //END redidual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
1048 
1049  //BEGIN redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1050  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1051  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1052 
1053  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1054  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1055  //LapvelVAR[idim] += GradSolVAR[dim+idim][jdim]*gradphi[i*dim+jdim];
1056  LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1057  AdvaleVAR[idim] += SolVAR[dim + jdim] * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] * phi[i];
1058  }
1059  }
1060 
1061  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1062  adept::adouble value = (-AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1063  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1064  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1065  ) * jacobian;
1066 
1067  if ((!solidmark[i])) {
1068  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value;
1069  }
1070  else {
1071  aRhs[indexVAR[dim+idim]][i] += value;
1072  }
1073 
1074  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1075  }
1076  }
1077  }
1078  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1079 
1080  //BEGIN continuity block
1081  {
1082  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
1083 
1084  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1085  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
1086  }
1087 
1088  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1089  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * jacobian;
1090  }
1091  }
1092  //END continuity block
1093  }
1094  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY
1095 
1096  //*******************************************************************************************************
1097 
1098  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY
1099  else {
1100  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1101  //physical quantity
1102  adept::adouble J_hat;
1103  adept::adouble I_e;
1104  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
1105  adept::adouble Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
1106 
1107  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
1108  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
1109 
1110  if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
1111  adept::adouble e[3][3];
1112 
1113  //computation of the stress tensor
1114  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1115  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1116  e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
1117  }
1118  }
1119 
1120  I_e = 0;
1121 
1122  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1123  I_e += e[i][i];
1124  }
1125 
1126  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1127  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1128  //incompressible
1129  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1130  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
1131  }
1132  }
1133  }
1134 
1135  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
1136  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1137  adept::adouble B[3][3];
1138 
1139  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1140  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1141  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
1142  }
1143  }
1144 
1145  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
1146  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
1147 
1148  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1149  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1150  B[I][J] = 0.;
1151 
1152  for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
1153  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
1154  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
1155  }
1156  }
1157  }
1158 
1159  if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
1160  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1161 
1162  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1163  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1164  if (1 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * B[I][J]
1165  - mus * I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
1166  else if (2 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus / J_hat * B[I][J]
1167  - mus / J_hat * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
1168  else if (3 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) / J_hat
1169  + lambda / J_hat * log(J_hat) * Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
1170  else if (4 == solid_model) Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - I1_B * Id2th[I][J] / 3.) / pow(J_hat, 5. / 3.)
1171  + lambda * (J_hat - 1.) * Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
1172 
1173  }
1174  }
1175  }
1176  else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
1177  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
1178  - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
1179  + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
1180  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
1181  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
1182 
1183  invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2]) * invdetB;
1184  invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1185  invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1186  invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1187  invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
1188  invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
1189  invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1190  invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1191  invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
1192 
1193  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1194  I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
1195  - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
1196 
1197  double C1 = mus / 3.;
1198  double C2 = C1 / 2.;
1199 
1200  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1201  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1202  Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
1203  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1204  - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1205  }
1206  }
1207 
1208  }
1209  }
1210 
1211  //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1212 
1213  //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1214  {
1215  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1216 
1217  //BEGIN redidual v=0 in fixed domain
1218  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1219  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (-phi[i] * (-SolVAR[dim + idim])) * jacobian_hat;
1220  }
1221 
1222  //END redidual v=0 in fixed domain
1223 
1224  //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1225  adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1226 
1227  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1228  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1229  CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
1230  }
1231  }
1232 
1233  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1234  aRhs[indexVAR[dim+idim]][i] += (phi[i] * _gravity[idim] - CauchyDIR[idim]) * jacobian;
1235  }
1236 
1237  //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1238  }
1239  }
1240  //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1241 
1242  //BEGIN continuity block
1243  {
1244  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1245  if (!penalty) {
1246  if (0 == solid_model) {
1247  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (I_e + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1248  }
1249  else if (1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model) {
1250  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * (J_hat - 1. + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim]) * jacobian_hat;
1251  }
1252  else if (2 == solid_model) {
1253  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (log(J_hat) / J_hat + (!incompressible) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1254  }
1255  }
1256  else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model) { // pressure = 0 in the solid
1257  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * (SolVAR[2 * dim])) * jacobian_hat;
1258  }
1259  }
1260  }
1261  //END continuity block
1262  }
1263 
1264  //END SOLID ASSEMBLY
1265  }
1266 
1267  //BEGIN local to global assembly
1268  //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
1269  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
1270  Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
1271 
1272  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
1273  Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
1274  }
1275  }

1277  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
1278 
1279  for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
1280  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
1281  }
1282 
1283  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
1284  myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
1285  }
1286 
1287  if( assembleMatrix ){
1288  //Store equations
1289  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
1290  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
1291  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
1292  }
1293 
1294  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
1295  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
1296 
1297  Jac.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
1298 
1299  s.jacobian(&Jac[0], true);
1300

1302  s.clear_independents();
1303  s.clear_dependents();
1304 
1305  //END local to global assembly
1306  }
1307  } //end list of elements loop

1310  myRES->close();

1315  end_time = clock();
1316  AssemblyTime += (end_time - start_time);
1317  // ***************** END ASSEMBLY RESIDUAL + MATRIX *******************
1318 
1319  }

469  ) * phi[i];
470 
471  AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
472  + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
473  ) * phi_old[i];
474  }
475  }
476 
477  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
478 
479  adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
480  - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
481 
482  adept::adouble value = theta * dt * (
483  - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
484  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
485  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
486  ) * Weight; // at time t
487 
488  adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * dt * (
489  - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
490  - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
491  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
492  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
493 
494  if (!solidmark[i]) {
495  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
496  }
497  else {
498  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
499  }
500 
501  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
502  }
503  }
504  }
505  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
506 
507  //BEGIN continuity block
508  {
509  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
510 
511  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
512  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
513  }
514 
515  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
516  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i] * div_vel) * Weight;
517  }
518  }
519  //END continuity block ===========================
520  }
521  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
522 
523  //*******************************************************************************************************
524 
525  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
526  else {
527  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
528  //physical quantity
529  adept::adouble J_hat;
530  double J_hat_old;
531  adept::adouble I_e;
532  double I_e_old;
533  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
534  adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
535  double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
536 
537 
538 
539 
540  if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
541  adept::adouble e[3][3];
542  double e_old[3][3];
543 
544  //computation of the stress tensor
545  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
546  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
547  e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
548  e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i]);
549  }
550  }
551 
552  I_e = 0;
553  I_e_old = 0;
554 
555  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
556  I_e += e[i][i];
557  I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
558  }
559 
560  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
561  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
562  //incompressible
563  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
564  Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR_old[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
565  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
566  }
567  }
568  }
569 
570  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
571 
572  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
573  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
574 
575  double I1_B_old = 0.;
576  double I2_B_old = 0.;
577 
578  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
579  adept::adouble B[3][3];
580 
581  double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
582  double B_old[3][3];
583 
584  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
585  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
586  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
587  F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
588  }
589  }
590 
591  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
592  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
593 
594  J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
595  + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
596  - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
597 
598 
599  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
600  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
601  B[I][J] = 0.;
602  B_old[I][J] = 0.;
603 
604  for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
605  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
606  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
607  B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
608  }
609  }
610  }
611 
612  if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
613  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
614  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
615 
616  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
617  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
618  if (1 == solid_model) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
619  Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
620  Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * (B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
621  }
622 
623 // else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
624 // -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
625 // else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
626 // + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
627 // else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
628 // + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
629 //
630  }
631  }
632  }
633  else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
634  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
635  - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
636  + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
637 
638  double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2])
639  - B_old[0][1] * (B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0])
640  + B_old[0][2] * (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]);
641 
642  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
643  double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
644  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
645  double invB_old[3][3];
646 
647  invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
648  invB[1][0] = -(B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
649  invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
650  invB[0][1] = -(B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
651  invB[1][1] = (B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;
652  invB[2][1] = -(B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2]) * invdetB;
653  invB[0][2] = (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
654  invB[1][2] = -(B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
655  invB[2][2] = (B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1]) * invdetB;
656 
657  invB_old[0][0] = (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
658  invB_old[1][0] = -(B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1]) * invdetB_old;
659  invB_old[2][0] = (B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
660  invB_old[0][1] = -(B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
661  invB_old[1][1] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0]) * invdetB_old;
662  invB_old[2][1] = -(B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2]) * invdetB_old;
663  invB_old[0][2] = (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]) * invdetB_old;
664  invB_old[1][2] = -(B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
665  invB_old[2][2] = (B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1]) * invdetB_old;
666 
667 
668  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
669  I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
670  - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
671 
672  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
673  I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
674  - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
675 
676  double C1 = mus / 3.;
677  double C2 = C1 / 2.;
678 
679  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
680  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
681  Cauchy[I][J] = 2.*(C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J])
682  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
683  - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
684 
685  Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* (C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J])

687  - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
688 
689  }
690  }
691 
692  }
693  }
694 
695  //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain

697  //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
698  {
699  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
700

705  ) * Weight_hat;
706  }

709

712  adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
713

717  CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
718  }
719  }
720

727  - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress

729

731  - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress

735  }

738  }

751  }

123  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++ ) {
124  Soli[i].reserve ( max_size );
125  Soli_old[i].reserve ( max_size );
126  dofsVAR[i].reserve ( max_size );
127  }
128 
129  vector< vector< double > > Rhs ( 2 * dim + 1 );
130  vector< vector< adept::adouble > > aRhs ( 2 * dim + 1 );
131 
132  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++ ) {
133  aRhs[i].reserve ( max_size );
134  Rhs[i].reserve ( max_size );
135  }
136 
137 
138  vector < int > dofsAll;
139  dofsAll.reserve ( max_size * ( 2 + dim + 1 ) );
140 
141  //vector < double > KKloc;
142  //KKloc.reserve ( dim * max_size * ( 2 * dim + 1 ) *dim * max_size * ( 2 * dim + 1 ) );
143 
144  vector < double > Jac;
145  Jac.reserve ( dim * max_size * ( 2 * dim + 1 ) *dim * max_size * ( 2 * dim + 1 ) );
146 
147  // ------------------------------------------------------------------------
148  // Physical parameters
149  double rhof = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ( "Fluid" ).get_density();
150  double rhos = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ( "Solid" ).get_density() / rhof;
151  double mu_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ( "Solid" ).get_lame_shear_modulus();
152  double lambda_lame = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ( "Solid" ).get_lame_lambda();
153  double mus = mu_lame / rhof;
154  double mu_lame1 = ml_prob.parameters.get < Solid> ( "Solid1" ).get_lame_shear_modulus();
155  double mus1 = mu_lame1 / rhof;
156  double IRe = ml_prob.parameters.get<Fluid> ( "Fluid" ).get_IReynolds_number();
157  double lambda = lambda_lame / rhof;
158  double betans = 1.;
159  int solid_model = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ( "Solid" ).get_physical_model();
160 
161  if ( solid_model >= 2 && solid_model <= 4 ) {
162  std::cout << "Error! Solid Model " << solid_model << "not implemented\n";
163  abort();
164  }
165 
166  bool incompressible = ( 0.5 == ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ( "Solid" ).get_poisson_coeff() ) ? 1 : 0;
167  const bool penalty = ml_prob.parameters.get<Solid> ( "Solid" ).get_if_penalty();
168 
169  // gravity
170  double _gravity[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
171 
172  double dt = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetIntervalTime();
173  double time = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetTime();
174  // -----------------------------------------------------------------
175  // space discretization parameters
176  unsigned SolType2 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType ( ml_sol->GetIndex ( "U" ) );
177  unsigned SolType1 = ml_sol->GetSolutionType ( ml_sol->GetIndex ( "P" ) );
178 
179  // mesh and procs
180  unsigned nel = mymsh->GetNumberOfElements();
181  unsigned igrid = mymsh->GetLevel();
182  unsigned iproc = mymsh->processor_id();
183 
184  unsigned indLmbd = ml_sol->GetIndex ( "lmbd" );
185 
186  //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
187  //variable-name handling
188  const char varname[7][3] = {"DX", "DY", "DZ", "U", "V", "W", "P"};
189  vector <unsigned> indexVAR ( 2 * dim + 1 );
190  vector <unsigned> indVAR ( 2 * dim + 1 );
191  vector <unsigned> SolType ( 2 * dim + 1 );
192 
193  for ( unsigned ivar = 0; ivar < dim; ivar++ ) {
194  indVAR[ivar] = ml_sol->GetIndex ( &varname[ivar][0] );
195  indVAR[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex ( &varname[ivar + 3][0] );
196  SolType[ivar] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType ( &varname[ivar][0] );
197  SolType[ivar + dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType ( &varname[ivar + 3][0] );
198  indexVAR[ivar] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex ( &varname[ivar][0] );
199  indexVAR[ivar + dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex ( &varname[ivar + 3][0] );
200  }
201 
202  indexVAR[2 * dim] = my_nnlin_impl_sys.GetSolPdeIndex ( &varname[6][0] );
203  indVAR[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetIndex ( &varname[6][0] );
204  SolType[2 * dim] = ml_sol->GetSolutionType ( &varname[6][0] );
205  //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
206 
207  int nprocs = mymsh->n_processors();
208  NumericVector * area_elem_first;
209  area_elem_first = NumericVector::build().release();
210 
211  if ( nprocs == 1 ) {
212  area_elem_first->init ( nprocs, 1, false, SERIAL );
213  }
214  else {
215  area_elem_first->init ( nprocs, 1, false, PARALLEL );
216  }
217 
218  area_elem_first->zero();
219  double rapresentative_area = 1.;
220 
221  start_time = clock();
222 
223  if ( assembleMatrix ) myKK->zero();
224 
225  // *** element loop ***
226  for ( int iel = mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]; iel < mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc + 1]; iel++ ) {
227 
228  short unsigned ielt = mymsh->GetElementType ( iel );
229  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber ( iel, SolType2 );
230  unsigned nve1 = mymsh->GetElementDofNumber ( iel, SolType1 );
231  int flag_mat = mymsh->GetElementMaterial ( iel );
232  unsigned elementGroup = mymsh->GetElementGroup ( iel );
233 
234  // *******************************************************************************************************
235 
236  //initialization of everything is in common fluid and solid
237 
238  //Rhs
239  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
240  dofsVAR[i].resize ( nve );
241  Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
242  Soli_old[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
243 
244  aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
245  // Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize ( nve );
246  }
247 
248  dofsVAR[2 * dim].resize ( nve1 );
249  Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
250  Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
251  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
252  // Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize ( nve1 );
253 
254  dofsAll.resize ( 0 );
255 
256  // KKloc.resize ( ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) * ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) );
257  Jac.resize ( ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) * ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 ) );
258 
259  // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
260  // coordinates, solutions, displacement, velocity dofs
261 
262  solidmark.resize ( nve );
263 
264  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
265  vx[i].resize ( nve );
266  vx_hat[i].resize ( nve );
267  vx_old[i].resize ( nve );
268  }
269 
270  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
271  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( i, iel, SolType2 );
272  // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
273  solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark ( idof ); // to check
274 
275  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
276  Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]] ) ( idof );
277  Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
278 
279  Soli_old[indexVAR[j]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j]] ) ( idof );
280  Soli_old[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
281 
282  aRhs[indexVAR[j]][i] = 0.;
283  aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
284 
285  //Fixed coordinates (Reference frame)
286  vx_hat[j][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[j] ) ( idof );
287  // displacement dofs
288  dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel );
289  // velocity dofs
290  dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel );
291  }
292  }
293 
294  // pressure dofs
295  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
296  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( i, iel, SolType[2 * dim] );
297  dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel );
298  Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
299  Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
300  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
301  }
302 
303  // build dof ccomposition
304  for ( int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++ ) {
305  dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end() );
306  }
307 
308  dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end() );
309 
310  //if (igrid==gridn || !myel->GetRefinedElementIndex(iel) ) {
311 
312  if ( assembleMatrix ) s.new_recording();
313 
314  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
315  for ( int j = 0; j < nve; j++ ) {
316  vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
317  vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][j];
318  }
319  }
320 
321  //Boundary integral
322  {
323 
324  vector < adept::adouble> normal ( dim, 0 );
325  vector < double > normal_old ( dim, 0 );
326 
327  // loop on faces
328  for ( unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber ( iel ); jface++ ) {
329  std::vector< double > xx ( dim, 0. );
330 
331  // look for boundary faces
332  if ( myel->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) < 0 ) {
333 
334  unsigned int face = - ( mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) + 1 );
335  double tau = 0.;
336  double tau_old = 0.;
337  if ( ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "P", tau, face, time ) &&
338  !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "P", tau_old, face, time - dt ) )
339  && ( tau != 0. || tau_old != 0. ) ) {
340 
341  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber ( iel, jface, SolType2 );
342  const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType ( iel, jface );
343 
344  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
345  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
346  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( ilocal, iel, 2 );
347 
348  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
349  vx_face[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
350  vx_face_old[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
351  }
352  }
353 
354  for ( unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++ ) {
355  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal );
356  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old );
357 
358  //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
359  // *** phi_i loop ***
360  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
361  adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
362  double value_old = - phi_old[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
363  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
364 
365  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
366  if ( ( !solidmark[ilocal] ) ) {
367  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
368  }
369  else { //if interface node it goes to solid
370  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
371  }
372  }
373  }
374  }
375  }
376  }
377  }
378  }
379 
380  // *** Gauss point loop ***
381  double area = 1.;
382 
383  for ( unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++ ) {
384  // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
385  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi );
386  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat );
387  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old );
388  phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi ( ig );
389 
390  if ( flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
391  if ( ig == 0 ) {
392  double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight ( ig );
393  area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
394 
395  if ( iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
396  area_elem_first->add ( mymsh->processor_id(), area );
397  area_elem_first->close();
398  rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
399  }
400  }
401 
402  Weight_nojac = Weight / area * rapresentative_area;
403 
404 // std::vector<double> xc(dim,0.);
405 // xc[0] = -0.001013;
406 // xc[1] = 0.07000;
407 // double distance = 0.;
408 // for (unsigned k = 0; k<dim; k++){
409 // distance += ( vx_hat[k][ nve - 1] - xc[k] ) * ( vx_hat[k][nve - 1] - xc[k] );
410 // }
411 // distance =sqrt(distance);
412 // Weight_nojac *= 1./(1 + 10000 * distance);
413 //
414 // if(elementGroup == 16) Weight_nojac *= 1.e06;
415  }
416 
417  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
418  // displacement and velocity
419  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
420  SolVAR[i] = 0.;
421  SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
422 
423  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
424  GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
425  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
426 
427  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
428  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
429  }
430 
431  for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
432  NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
433  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
434  }
435 
436  for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++ ) {
437  SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
438  SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
439 
440  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
441  GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
442  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
443 
444  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
445  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
446  }
447  for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
448  NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
449  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] += nablaphi_old[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
450  }
451  }
452  }
453 
454  // pressure
455  SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
456 
457  for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++ ) {
458  SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
459  }
460 
461  // Lagrangian mesh velocity at t = time + dt/2
462  vector < adept::adouble > meshVel ( dim );
463  vector < vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel ( dim );
464 
465  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
466  meshVel[i] = ( SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i] ) / dt;
467  GradMeshVel[i].resize ( dim );
468 
469  for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
470  GradMeshVel[i][j] = ( GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j] ) / dt;
471  }
472  }
473 
474  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
475  //BEGIN FLUID and POROUS MEDIA ASSEMBLY ============
476  if ( flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 ) {
477 
478  vector < adept::adouble > a ( dim );
479  vector < adept::adouble > a_old ( dim );
480  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
481  a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i]; // TODO maybe we subtract meshVel[i] maybe not
482  a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i];
483  }
484 
485  // speed
486  adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
487  adept::adouble a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
488  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
489  aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
490  a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
491  }
492  aL2Norm = sqrt ( aL2Norm );
493  a_oldL2Norm = sqrt ( a_oldL2Norm );
494 
495  double sqrtlambdak = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd] ) ( iel );
496  adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
497  adept::adouble tauSupg_old = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
498  adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
499  adept::adouble Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
500 
501  if ( Rek > 1.0e-15 ) {
502  adept::adouble xiRek = ( Rek >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek;
503  tauSupg = xiRek / ( aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
504  }
505 
506  if ( Rek_old > 1.0e-15 ) {
507  adept::adouble xiRek_old = ( Rek_old >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek_old;
508  tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / ( a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
509  }
510 
511  //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
512 
513 
514  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg ( nve, 0. );
515  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg_old ( nve, 0. );
516  //tauSupg=0;
517  //tauSupg_old=0;
518  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
519  for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
520  phiSupg[i] += ( ( SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg;// * (!solidmark[i]) ;
521  phiSupg_old[i] += ( ( SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg_old;// * (!solidmark[i]);
522  }
523  }
524 
525 
526  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
527  {
528  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
529 
530  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
531  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
532 
533  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
534  for ( int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
535  //LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] ) * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
536  LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + 0.*GradSolVAR[jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
537  }
538  }
539 
540  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
541  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += ( !solidmark[i] ) * ( - LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac );
542  }
543 
544  //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
545 
546  if ( flag_mat == 2 ) {
547  //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
548  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
549  adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
550  adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
551  adept::adouble LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
552  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
553  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
554 
555  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
556  for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
557  unsigned kdim;
558  if ( idim == jdim ) kdim = jdim;
559  else if ( 1 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim; // xy
560  else if ( 2 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
561  else if ( 3 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
562  //laplaciano debole
563  LapvelVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
564  LapvelVAR_old[idim] += ( GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
565  //laplaciano strong
566  LapStrong[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg[i];
567  LapStrong_old[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg_old[i];
568 
569  AdvaleVAR[idim] += ( ( SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
570  + ( 0.*GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
571  //) * phi[i];
572  ) * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] );
573 
574  AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ( ( SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
575  + (0.*GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
576  //) * phi_old[i];
577  ) * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] );
578  }
579  }
580 
581  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
582 
583  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] ) * Weight
584  - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] ) * Weight_old )/dt;
585 
586  adept::adouble value = theta * (
587  - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
588  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
589  + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
590  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
591  ) * Weight; // at time t
592 
593  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * (
594  - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
595  - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
596  + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
597  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
598  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
599 
600  if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
601  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
602  }
603  else {
604  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
605  }
606 
607  }
608  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
609  }
610  else if ( flag_mat == 3 ) {
611  //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
612 
613 
614  adept::adouble speed = 0.;
615  adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
616  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
617  speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
618  speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
619  }
620  double eps = 1.0e-12;
621  speed = sqrt ( speed + eps );
622  speed_old = sqrt ( speed_old + eps );
623  double DE = 0.;
624  if ( dim == 2 ) {
625  DE = 0.0002; // AAA_thrombus_2D
626  //DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
627  }
628  else if ( dim == 3 ) {
629  DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
630  }
631  double b = 4188;
632  double a = 1452;
633  double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
634  double C2 = 2 * a / ( rhof * DE );
635 
636 
637 
638 
639 
640 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
641 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
642 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
643 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
644 //
645 // for(int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
646 // for(int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
647 //
648 // LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
649 // LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
650 //
651 // AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
652 // + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
653 // ) * phi[i];
654 //
655 // AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
656 // + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
657 // ) * phi_old[i];
658 // }
659 // }
660 
661  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
662 
663 // adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
664 // - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
665 
666  adept::adouble value = theta * (
667 // - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
668 // - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
669  //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
670  - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
671  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
672  ) * Weight; // at time t
673 
674  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * (
675 // - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
676 // - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
677  //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]
678  - (SolVAR_old[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i])
679  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
680  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
681 
682  if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
683  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value + value_old;
684  }
685  else {
686  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value + value_old;
687  }
688 
689  }
690  //END redidual Porous Media in moving domain
691  }
692  }
693  }
694  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
695 
696  //BEGIN continuity block
697  {
698  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
699 
700  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
701  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
702  }
703 
704  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
705  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * div_vel ) * Weight;
706  }
707  }
708  //END continuity block ===========================
709  }
710  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
711 
712  //*******************************************************************************************************
713 
714  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
715  else {
716  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
717  //physical quantity
718  adept::adouble J_hat;
719  double J_hat_old;
720  adept::adouble I_e;
721  double I_e_old;
722  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
723  adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
724  double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
725 
726 
727 
728 
729  if ( solid_model == 0 ) { // Saint-Venant
730  adept::adouble e[3][3];
731  double e_old[3][3];
732 
733  //computation of the stress tensor
734  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
735  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
736  e[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i] );
737  e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i] );
738  }
739  }
740 
741  I_e = 0;
742  I_e_old = 0;
743 
744  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
745  I_e += e[i][i];
746  I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
747  }
748 
749  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
750  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
751  //incompressible
752  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
753  Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
754  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
755  }
756  }
757  }
758 
759  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
760 
761  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
762  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
763 
764  double I1_B_old = 0.;
765  double I2_B_old = 0.;
766 
767  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
768  adept::adouble B[3][3];
769 
770  double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
771  double B_old[3][3];
772 
773  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
774  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
775  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
776  F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
777  }
778  }
779 
780  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
781  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
782 
783  J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
784  + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
785  - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
786 
787 
788  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
789  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
790  B[I][J] = 0.;
791  B_old[I][J] = 0.;
792 
793  for ( int K = 0; K < 3; ++K ) {
794  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
795  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
796  B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
797  }
798  }
799  }
800 
801  if ( solid_model <= 4 ) { // Neo-Hookean
802  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
803  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
804 
805  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
806  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
807  if ( 1 == solid_model ) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
808  Cauchy[I][J] = mus * ( B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
809  Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * ( B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
810  }
811 
812 // else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
813 // -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
814 // else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
815 // + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
816 // else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
817 // + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
818 //
819  }
820  }
821  }
822  else if ( 5 == solid_model ) { //Mooney-Rivlin
823  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2] )
824  - B[0][1] * ( B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] )
825  + B[0][2] * ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] );
826 
827  double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2] )
828  - B_old[0][1] * ( B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] )
829  + B_old[0][2] * ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] );
830 
831  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
832  double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
833  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
834  double invB_old[3][3];
835 
836  invB[0][0] = ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
837  invB[1][0] = - ( B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
838  invB[2][0] = ( B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
839  invB[0][1] = - ( B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
840  invB[1][1] = ( B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
841  invB[2][1] = - ( B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2] ) * invdetB;
842  invB[0][2] = ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
843  invB[1][2] = - ( B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
844  invB[2][2] = ( B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
845 
846  invB_old[0][0] = ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
847  invB_old[1][0] = - ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
848  invB_old[2][0] = ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
849  invB_old[0][1] = - ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
850  invB_old[1][1] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
851  invB_old[2][1] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2] ) * invdetB_old;
852  invB_old[0][2] = ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
853  invB_old[1][2] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
854  invB_old[2][2] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
855 
856 
857  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
858  I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
859  - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
860 
861  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
862  I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
863  - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
864 
865  //double C1 = mus / 3.;
866  double C1 = ( elementGroup == 15 ) ? mus1 / 3. : mus / 3.;
867  double C2 = C1 / 2.;
868 
869  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
870  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
871  Cauchy[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J] )
872  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
873  - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
874 
875  Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J] )
876  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B_old - C2 * I2_B_old) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
877  - 1. / rhof * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
878 
879  }
880  }
881 
882  }
883  }
884 
885  //END build Cauchy Stress in moving domain
886 
887  //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
888  {
889  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
890 
891  //BEGIN redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
892  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
893  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += - phi[i] * ( (-SolVAR[idim] + SolVAR_old[idim])/dt +
894  ( theta * SolVAR[dim + idim] + ( 1. - theta ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] )
895  ) * Weight_hat;
896  }
897 
898  //END redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
899 
900  //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
901  adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
902  adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
903 
904  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
905  for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
906  CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
907  CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
908  }
909  }
910 
911  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
912 
913  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( rhos * SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
914  - rhos * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old )/dt;
915 
916  adept::adouble value = theta * ( rhos * phi[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
917  - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress
918  ) * Weight; // at time t
919 
920  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * ( rhos * phi_old[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
921  - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress
922  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
923 
924  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
925  }
926 
927  //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
928  }
929  }
930  //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
931 
932  //BEGIN continuity block
933  {
934  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
935  if ( !penalty ) {
936  if ( 0 == solid_model ) {
937  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * ( I_e + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) ) * Weight_hat;
938  }
939  else if ( 1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model ) {
940  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * ( J_hat - 1. + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) * Weight_hat;
941  }
942 
943 // else if (2 == solid_model){
944 // aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( log(J_hat)/J_hat + (!incompressible)/lambda*SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
945 // }
946  }
947 
948 // else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model){ // pressure = 0 in the solid
949 // aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
950 // }
951  }
952  }
953  //END continuity block
954  }
955 
956  //END SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
957  }
958 
959  //}
960 
961  //BEGIN local to global assembly
962  //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
963  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
964  Rhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
965 
966  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
967  Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
968  }
969  }
970 
971  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]].resize(nve1);
972 
973  for (unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++) {
974  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = -aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
975  }
976 
977  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++) {
978  myRES->add_vector_blocked(Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i]);
979  }
980 
981  if (assembleMatrix) {
982  //Store equations
983  for (int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++) {
984  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
985  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve);
986  }
987 
988  s.dependent(&aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
989  s.independent(&Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1);
990 
991  Jac.resize((2 * dim * nve + nve1) * (2 * dim * nve + nve1));
992 
993  s.jacobian(&Jac[0], true);
994 
995  myKK->add_matrix_blocked(Jac, dofsAll, dofsAll);
996  s.clear_independents();
997  s.clear_dependents();
998 
999  //END local to global assembly
1000  }
1001  } //end list of elements loop
1002 
1003 
1004 
1005 
1006 // //BEGIN local to global assembly
1007 // //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
1008 // for ( unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
1009 // for ( int j = 0; j < nve; j++ ) {
1010 // Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
1011 // }
1012 // }
1013 //
1014 // for ( unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++ ) {
1015 // Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
1016 // }
1017 //
1018 // for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++ ) {
1019 // myRES->add_vector_blocked ( Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i] );
1020 // }
1021 //
1022 // if ( assembleMatrix ) {
1023 // //Store equations
1024 // for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
1025 // s.dependent ( &aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve );
1026 // s.independent ( &Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve );
1027 // }
1028 //
1029 // s.dependent ( &aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1 );
1030 // s.independent ( &Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1 );
1031 // s.jacobian ( &Jac[0] );
1032 // unsigned nveAll = ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 );
1033 //
