1568  meshVel[i] = (SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i]) / dt;
1569  GradMeshVel[i].resize(dim);
1570 
1571  for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1572  GradMeshVel[i][j] = (GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j]) / dt;
1573  }
1574  }
1575 
1576  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1577  //BEGIN FLUID and POROUS MEDIA ASSEMBLY ============
1578  if (flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3) {
1579 
1580  vector < adept::adouble > a(dim);
1581  vector < adept::adouble > a_old(dim);
1582  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1583  a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i]; // TODO maybe we subtract meshVel[i] maybe not
1584  a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim] - 0.*meshVel[i];
1585  }
1586 
1587  // speed
1588  adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
1589  adept::adouble a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
1590  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1591  aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
1592  a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
1593  }
1594  aL2Norm = sqrt(aL2Norm);
1595  a_oldL2Norm = sqrt(a_oldL2Norm);
1596 
1597  double sqrtlambdak = (*mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd])(iel);
1598  adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
1599  adept::adouble tauSupg_old = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
1600  adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
1601  adept::adouble Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
1602 
1603  if (Rek > 1.0e-15) {
1604  adept::adouble xiRek = (Rek >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek;
1605  tauSupg = xiRek / (aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
1606  }
1607 
1608  if (Rek_old > 1.0e-15) {
1609  adept::adouble xiRek_old = (Rek_old >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek_old;
1610  tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / (a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
1611  }
1612 
1613  //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
1614 
1615 
1616  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg(nve, 0.);
1617  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg_old(nve, 0.);
1618  //tauSupg=0;
1619  //tauSupg_old=0;
1620  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1621  for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1622  phiSupg[i] += ((SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j]) * gradphi[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg; // * (!solidmark[i]) ;
1623  phiSupg_old[i] += ((SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel[j]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg_old; // * (!solidmark[i]);
1624  }
1625  }
1626 
1627 
1628  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1629  {
1630  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
1631 
1632  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
1633 
1634 
1635  if (!solidmark[i]) {
1636  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1637  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1638  for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1639  //LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] ) * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
1640  LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + 0.*GradSolVAR[jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1641  }
1642  }
1643 
1644  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1645  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (- LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac);
1646  }
1647  }
1648 
1649  //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
1650 
1651  if (flag_mat == 2) {
1652  //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1653  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1654  adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1655  adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1656  adept::adouble LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1657  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1658  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1659 
1660  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1661  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1662  unsigned kdim;
1663  if (idim == jdim) kdim = jdim;
1664  else if (1 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim; // xy
1665  else if (2 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
1666  else if (3 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
1667  //laplaciano debole
1668  LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1669  LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1670  //laplaciano strong
1671  LapStrong[idim] += (NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg[i];
1672  LapStrong_old[idim] += (NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg_old[i];
1673 
1674  AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1675  + (0.*GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1676  //) * phi[i];
1677  ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]);
1678 
1679  AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1680  + (0.*GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1681  //) * phi_old[i];
1682  ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]);
1683  }
1684  }
1685 
1686  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1687 
1688  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - (SolVAR[dim + idim] * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]) * Weight
1689  - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]) * Weight_old) / dt;
1690 
1691  adept::adouble value = theta * (
1692  - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1693  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1694  + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
1695  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1696  ) * Weight; // at time t
1697 
1698  adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
1699  - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1700  - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1701  + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
1702  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1703  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1704 
1705  if (!solidmark[i]) {
1706  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1707  }
1708  else {
1709  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1710  }
1711 
1712  }
1713  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1714  }
1715  else if (flag_mat == 3) {
1716  //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1717 
1718 
1719  adept::adouble speed = 0.;
1720  adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
1721  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1722  speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
1723  speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
1724  }
1725  double eps = 1.0e-12;
1726  speed = sqrt(speed + eps);
1727  speed_old = sqrt(speed_old + eps);
1728  double DE = 0.;
1729  if (dim == 2) {
1730  DE = 0.0002; // AAA_thrombus_2D
1731  //DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
1732  }
1733  else if (dim == 3) {
1734  DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
1735  }
1736  double b = 4188;
1737  double a = 1452;
1738  double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
1739  double C2 = 2 * a / (rhof * DE);
1740 
1741 
1742 
1743 
1744 
1745 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1746 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1747 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1748 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1749 //
1750 // for(int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1751 // for(int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1752 //
1753 // LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1754 // LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1755 //
1756 // AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1757 // + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1758 // ) * phi[i];
1759 //
1760 // AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1761 // + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1762 // ) * phi_old[i];
1763 // }
1764 // }
1765 
1766  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1767 
1768 // adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
1769 // - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
1770 
1771  adept::adouble value = theta * (
1772 // - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1773 // - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1774  //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
1775  - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * (IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
1776  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1777  ) * Weight; // at time t
1778 
1779  adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
1780 // - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1781 // - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1782  //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]
1783  - (SolVAR_old[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * (IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i])
1784  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1785  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1786 
1787  if (!solidmark[i]) {
1788  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1789  }
1790  else {
1791  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1792  }
1793 
1794  }
1795  //END redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1796  }
1797 
1798  if (auxDisp) {
1799  //BEGIN auxiliary displacement equation
1800  adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1801 
1802  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1803  for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1804  LapAuxVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] + 0. * GradSolVAR[jdim + 2 * dim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1805  }
1806  }
1807 
1808  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1809  aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1810  }
1811 // for (int idim = 1; idim < dim; idim++) {
1812 // aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1813 // }
1814 // for (int idim = 1; idim < dim; idim++) {
1815 // aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( meshIsCurrupted * 1.0e-1 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + 0 * ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi[i] ) * Weight_nojac;
1816 // }
1817 
1818 // adept::adouble LapAuxVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1819 //
1820 // for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1821 // for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1822 // LapAuxVAR[idim] += GradSolhatVAR[idim + 2 * dim][jdim] * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
1823 // }
1824 // }
1825 //
1826 // for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
1827 // aRhs[indexVAR[idim + 2 * dim]][i] += ( 1.0e-10 * LapAuxVAR[idim] + ( SolVAR[idim + 2 * dim] - SolVAR[idim] ) * phi_hat[i] ) * Weight_hat;
1828 // }
1829 
1830 
1831  //END auxiliary displacement equation
1832  }
1833 
1834  }
1835  }
1836  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1837 
1838 
1839 
1840 
1841 
1842  //BEGIN continuity block
1843  {
1844  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
1845 
1846  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1847  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
1848  }
1849 
1850  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
1851  aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] += - (-phi1[i] * div_vel) * Weight;
1852  }
1853  }
1854  //END continuity block ===========================
1855  }
1856  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
1857 
1858  //*******************************************************************************************************
1859 
1860  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
1861  else {
1862  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1863  //physical quantity
1864  adept::adouble J_hat;
1865  adept::adouble J_hat1;
1866  double J_hat_old;
1867  adept::adouble I_e;
1868  double I_e_old;
1869  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
1870  adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
1871  double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
1872 
1873 
1874 
1875 
1876  if (solid_model == 0) { // Saint-Venant
1877  adept::adouble e[3][3];
1878  double e_old[3][3];
1879 
1880  //computation of the stress tensor
1881  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1882  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1883  e[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i]);
1884  e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * (GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i]);
1885  }
1886  }
1887 
1888  I_e = 0;
1889  I_e_old = 0;
1890 
1891  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1892  I_e += e[i][i];
1893  I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
1894  }
1895 
1896  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1897  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1898  //incompressible
1899  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1900  Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1901  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
1902  }
1903  }
1904  }
1905 
1906  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
1907 
1908  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
1909  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
1910 
1911  double I1_B_old = 0.;
1912  double I2_B_old = 0.;
1913 
1914  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1915  adept::adouble F1[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1916  adept::adouble B[3][3];
1917 
1918  double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1919  double B_old[3][3];
1920 
1921  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
1922  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
1923  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
1924  F1[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i + 2 * dim][j];
1925  F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
1926  }
1927  }
1928 
1929  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
1930  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
1931 
1932  J_hat1 = F1[0][0] * F1[1][1] * F1[2][2] + F1[0][1] * F1[1][2] * F1[2][0] + F1[0][2] * F1[1][0] * F1[2][1]
1933  - F1[2][0] * F1[1][1] * F1[0][2] - F1[2][1] * F1[1][2] * F1[0][0] - F1[2][2] * F1[1][0] * F1[0][1];
1934 
1935  J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
1936  + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
1937  - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
1938 
1939 
1940  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1941  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1942  B[I][J] = 0.;
1943  B_old[I][J] = 0.;
1944 
1945  for (int K = 0; K < 3; ++K) {
1946  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
1947  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
1948  B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
1949  }
1950  }
1951  }
1952 
1953  if (solid_model <= 4) { // Neo-Hookean
1954  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1955  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
1956 
1957  for (int I = 0; I < 3; ++I) {
1958  for (int J = 0; J < 3; ++J) {
1959  if (1 == solid_model) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
1960  Cauchy[I][J] = mus * (B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1961  Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * (B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J]) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1962  }
1963 
1964 // else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
1965 // -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
1966 // else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
1967 // + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
1968 // else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
1969 // + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
1970 //
1971  }
1972  }
1973  }
1974  else if (5 == solid_model) { //Mooney-Rivlin
1975  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2])
1976  - B[0][1] * (B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0])
1977  + B[0][2] * (B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1]);
1978 
1979  double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * (B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2])
1980  - B_old[0][1] * (B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0])
1981  + B_old[0][2] * (B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1]);
1982 
1983  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
1984  double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
1985  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
1986  double invB_old[3][3];
1987 
1988  invB[0][0] = (B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1989  invB[1][0] = - (B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1]) * invdetB;
1990  invB[2][0] = (B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1]) * invdetB;
1991  invB[0][1] = - (B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0]) * invdetB;

259  unsigned elementGroup = mymsh->GetElementGroup(iel);
260 
261  // *******************************************************************************************************
262 
263  //initialization of everything is in common fluid and solid
264 
265  //Rhs
266  for (int i = 0; i < nBlocks * dim; i++) {
267  dofsVAR[i].resize(nve);
268  Soli[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
269  Soli_old[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
270  aRhs[indexVAR[i]].resize(nve);
271  }
272  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
273  meshVelOldNode[i].resize(nve);
274  }
275 
276  dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].resize(nve1);
277  Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
278  Soli_old[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
279  aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]].resize(nve1);
280 
281  dofsAll.resize(0);
282 
283  Jac.resize((nBlocks * dim * nve + nve1) * (nBlocks * dim * nve + nve1));
284 
285  // ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
286  // coordinates, solutions, displacement, velocity dofs
287 
288  solidmark.resize(nve);
289 
290  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
291  vx[i].resize(nve);
292  vx_hat[i].resize(nve);
293  vx_old[i].resize(nve);
294  }
295 
296  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
297  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType2);
298  // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
299  solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark(idof); // to check
300 
301  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
302  for (unsigned k = 0; k < nBlocks; k++) {
303  Soli[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + k * dim]])(idof);
304  Soli_old[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + k * dim]])(idof);
305  aRhs[indexVAR[j + k * dim]][i] = 0.;
306  dofsVAR[j + k * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[j + k * dim], indexVAR[j + k * dim], i, iel);
307  }
308  meshVelOldNode[j][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR2[j]])(idof);
309  vx_hat[j][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[j])(idof);
310  }
311  }
312 
313 
314  // pressure dofs
315  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++) {
316  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(i, iel, SolType[nBlocks * dim]);
317  dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof(indVAR[nBlocks * dim], indexVAR[nBlocks * dim], i, iel);
318  Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[nBlocks * dim]])(idof);
319  Soli_old[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = (*mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[nBlocks * dim]])(idof);
320  aRhs[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][i] = 0.;
321  }
322 
323  // build dof ccomposition
324  for (int idim = 0; idim < nBlocks * dim; idim++) {
325  dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end());
326  }
327  dofsAll.insert(dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[nBlocks * dim].end());
328 
329  if (assembleMatrix) s.new_recording();
330 
331 
332  for (int j = 0; j < nve; j++) {
333  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(j, iel, SolType2);
334  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
335  vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
336  vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][j];
337  }
338  }
339 
340  //Boundary integral
341  {
342 
343  vector < adept::adouble> normal(dim, 0);
344  vector < double > normal_old(dim, 0);
345 
346  // loop on faces
347  for (unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber(iel); jface++) {
348  std::vector< double > xx(dim, 0.);
349 
350  // look for boundary faces
351  if (myel->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) < 0) {
352 
353  unsigned int face = - (mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex(iel, jface) + 1);
354  double tau = 0.;
355  double tau_old = 0.;
356  if ((!ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "P", tau, face, time) &&
357  !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction()(xx, "P", tau_old, face, time - dt))
358  && (tau != 0. || tau_old != 0.)) {
359 
360  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber(iel, jface, SolType2);
361  const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType(iel, jface);
362 
363  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
364  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
365  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof(ilocal, iel, 2);
366 
367  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
368  vx_face[idim][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
369  vx_face_old[idim][i] = (*mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim])(idof) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
370  }
371  }
372 
373  for (unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++) {
374  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal);
375  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur(vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old);
376 
377  //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
378  // *** phi_i loop ***
379  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
380  adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
381  double value_old = - phi_old[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
382  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex(iel, jface, i);
383 
384  for (unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
385  if ((!solidmark[ilocal])) {
386  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += (theta * value + (1. - theta) * value_old) * normal[idim];
387  }
388  else { //if interface node it goes to solid
389  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += (theta * value + (1. - theta) * value_old) * normal[idim];
390  }
391  }
392  }
393  }
394  }
395  }
396  }
397  }
398 
399 
400  // *** Gauss point loop ***
401  double area = 1.;
402 
403  for (unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++) {
404  // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
405  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi);
406  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat);
407  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian(vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old);
408  phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi(ig);
409 
410  if (flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
411  if (ig == 0) {
412  double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight(ig);
413  area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
414 
415  if (iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc]) {
416  area_elem_first->add(mymsh->processor_id(), area);
417  area_elem_first->close();
418  rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
419  }
420  }
421 
422  Weight_nojac = Weight;// / area * 1.e-10;// * rapresentative_area;
423 
424  //-----------------------------------------------------------------------//
425  // for vein_valve mesh
426  std::vector<double> xc(dim, 0.);
427  //xc[0] = -0.001013; // vein_valve
428  //xc[1] = 0.07000;
429 // xc[0] = -0.000286; // vein_valve_closed
430 // xc[1] = 0.07000;
431 //
432 // if (dim == 2) {
433 // xc[0] = -0.00025; // vein_valve_closed in valve2.neu
434 // xc[1] = 0.07000;
435 // }
436 // if (dim == 2) {
437 // xc[0] = -0.000220; // vein_valve_closed valve2_corta.neu
438 // xc[1] = 0.068718;
439 // }
440  if (dim == 2) {
441  xc[0] = -0.000193; // vein_valve_closed valve2_corta2.neu
442  xc[1] = 0.067541*0;
443  }
444 // else if (dim == 3){
445 // xc[0] = -0.008; // vein_valve_closed
446 // xc[1] = 0.0;
447 // }
448  else if (dim == 3) {
449  xc[0] = 0.0015; // vein_valve_closed
450  xc[1] = 0.0;
451  xc[2] = 0.01;
452  }
453 
454  double distance = 0.;
455  for (unsigned k = 0; k < dim; k++) {
456  distance += (vx_hat[k][ nve - 1] - xc[k]) * (vx_hat[k][nve - 1] - xc[k]);
457  }
458  distance = sqrt(distance);
459  Weight_nojac *= 1. / (1 + 10000 * distance);
460 
461  if (elementGroup == 16) Weight_nojac *= 100;
462  //-----------------------------------------------------------------------//
463  }
464 
465  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
466  // displacement and velocity
467 
468  for (int i = 0; i < nBlocks * dim; i++) {
469  SolVAR[i] = 0.;
470  SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
471 
472  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
473  GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
474  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
475 
476  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
477  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
478  }
479 
480  for (int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++) {
481  NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
482  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
483  }
484 
485  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
486  SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
487  SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
488 
489  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
490  GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
491  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
492 
493  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
494  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
495  }
496  for (int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++) {
497  NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
498  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] += nablaphi_old[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
499  }
500  }
501  }
502 
503  // pressure
504  SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] = 0.;
505  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++) {
506  SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[nBlocks * dim]][inode];
507  }
508 
509  vector < adept::adouble > vx_ig(dim);
510  vector < double > vxOld_ig(dim);
511 
512  // mesh velocity OLD
513  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
514  vx_ig[i]=0.;
515  vxOld_ig[i]=0.;
516  meshVel_old[i] = 0.;
517  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
518  GradMeshVel_old[i][j] = 0.;
519  }
520  for (unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++) {
521  vx_ig[i]+=phi[inode] * vx[i][inode];
522  vxOld_ig[i]+=phi[inode] * vx_old[i][inode];
523  meshVel_old[i] += phi[inode] * meshVelOldNode[i][inode];
524  for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
525  GradMeshVel_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * meshVelOldNode[i][inode];//TODO
526  }
527  }
528  }
529 
530  // mesh velocity NEW
531  vector < adept::adouble > meshVel(dim);
532  vector < vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel(dim);
533  for (unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
534  meshVel[i] = 2./dt * (SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i]) - meshVel_old[i];
535  GradMeshVel[i].resize(dim);
536  for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
537  GradMeshVel[i][j] = 2./dt * (GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j]) - GradMeshVel_old[i][j];
538  }
539  }
540 
541  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
542  //BEGIN FLUID and POROUS MEDIA ASSEMBLY ============
543  if (flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3) {
544 
545  vector < adept::adouble > a(dim);
546  vector < double > a_old(dim);
547 
548  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
549  a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim];// - 0.*meshVel[i]; // TODO maybe we subtract meshVel[i] maybe not
550  a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim];// - 0.*meshVel[i];
551  }
552 
553  // speed
554  adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
555  double a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
556  for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++) {
557  aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
558  a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
559  }
560  aL2Norm = sqrt(aL2Norm);
561  a_oldL2Norm = sqrt(a_oldL2Norm);
562 
563  double sqrtlambdak = (*mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd])(iel);
564  adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
565  double tauSupg_old = 1. / (sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe);
566  adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
567  double Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / (4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe);
568 
569  if (Rek > 1.0e-15) {
570  adept::adouble xiRek = (Rek >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek;
571  tauSupg = xiRek / (aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
572  }
573 
574  if (Rek_old > 1.0e-15) {
575  double xiRek_old = (Rek_old >= 1.) ? 1. : Rek_old;
576  tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / (a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak);
577  }
578 
579  //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
580 
581  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg(nve, 0.);
582  vector < double > phiSupg_old(nve, 0.);
583  //tauSupg=0;
584  //tauSupg_old=0;
585  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
586  for (unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++) {
587  phiSupg[i] += ((SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j]) * gradphi[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg; // * (!solidmark[i]) ;
588  phiSupg_old[i] += ((SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel_old[j]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j]) * tauSupg_old; // * (!solidmark[i]);
589  }
590  }
591 
592 
593  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
594  {
595  for (unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++) {
596 
597  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
598 
599 
600  if (!solidmark[i]) {
601  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
602  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
603  for (int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
604  //LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] ) * gradphi_hat[i * dim + jdim];
605  LapmapVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + 0.*GradSolVAR[jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
606  }
607  }
608 
609  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
610  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += (- LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac);
611  }
612  }
613 
614  //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
615 
616  if (flag_mat == 2) {
617  //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
618  adept::adouble Lapdisp[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
619  adept::adouble Lapdisp_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
620  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
621  double LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
622  adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
623  double LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
624  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
625  double AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
626 
627  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
628  for (int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
629  unsigned kdim;
630  if (idim == jdim) kdim = jdim;
631  else if (1 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim; // xy
632  else if (2 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
633  else if (3 == idim + jdim) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
634  //laplaciano debole
635  LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
636  LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
637 
638  Lapdisp[idim] += (GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
639  Lapdisp_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
640 
641  //laplaciano strong
642  LapStrong[idim] += (NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg[i];
643  LapStrong_old[idim] += (NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim]) * phiSupg_old[i];
644 
645  AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
646  + ((dim==2)*GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
647  ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]);
648 
649  AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel_old[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
650  + ((dim==2)*GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel_old[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
651  ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]);
652  }
653  }
654 
655  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
656 
657  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - (SolVAR[dim + idim] * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i]) * Weight
658  - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i]) * Weight_old) / dt;
659 
660  adept::adouble value = theta * (
661  - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
662  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
663  - (idim == 0) * Lapdisp[idim] * 1.e-3 * exp( (vx_ig[0] + 2.5e-5)/0.0001)*(dim==2)
664  - (idim == 0) * Lapdisp[idim] * 1.e-1 * exp(-(vx_ig[0] - 1e-4)/0.00004)*(dim==3)
665  + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
666  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
667  ) * Weight; // at time t
668 
669  adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
670  - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
671  - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
672  - (idim == 0) * Lapdisp_old[idim] * 1.e-3 * exp( (vxOld_ig[0] + 2.5e-5)/0.0001)*(dim==2)
673  - (idim == 0) * Lapdisp_old[idim] * 1.e-1 * exp(-(vxOld_ig[0] - 1.e-4)/0.0004)*(dim==3)
674  + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
675  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
676  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
677 
678  if (!solidmark[i]) {
679  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
680  }
681  else {
682  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
683  }
684 
685  }
686  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
687  }
688  else if (flag_mat == 3) {
689  //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
690 
691 
692  adept::adouble speed = 0.;
693  adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
694  for (int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
695  speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
696  speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
697  }
698  double eps = 1.0e-12;
699  speed = sqrt(speed + eps);
700  speed_old = sqrt(speed_old + eps);
701  double DE = 0.;
702  if (dim == 2) {
703  DE = 0.0002; // AAA_thrombus_2D
704  //DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
705  }
706  else if (dim == 3) {
707  DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
708  }
709  double b = 4188;
710  double a = 1452;
711  double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
712  double C2 = 2 * a / (rhof * DE);
713 
714  for (int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++) {
715 
716 // adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
717 // - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
718 
719  adept::adouble value = theta * (
720 // - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
721 // - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
722  //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
723  - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * (IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
724  + 1. / rhof * SolVAR[nBlocks * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
725  ) * Weight; // at time t
726 
727  adept::adouble value_old = (1. - theta) * (
728 // - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
729 // - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
730  //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]

1313  solidmark.resize ( nve );

1316  vx[i].resize ( nve );
1317  vx_hat[i].resize ( nve );
1318  vx_old[i].resize ( nve );
1319  }

1323  // flag to know if the node "idof" lays on the fluid-solid interface
1324  solidmark[i] = mymsh->GetSolidMark ( idof ); // to check
1325 
1326  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1327  Soli[indexVAR[j]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j]] ) ( idof );
1328  Soli[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
1329

1331  Soli_old[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[j + dim]] ) ( idof );
1332

1334  aRhs[indexVAR[j + dim]][i] = 0.;
1335

1337  vx_hat[j][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[j] ) ( idof );
1338  // displacement dofs
1339  dofsVAR[j][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j], indexVAR[j], i, iel );
1340  // velocity dofs
1341  dofsVAR[j + dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[j + dim], indexVAR[j + dim], i, iel );
1342  }

1346  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
1347  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( i, iel, SolType[2 * dim] );
1348  dofsVAR[2 * dim][i] = myLinEqSolver->GetSystemDof ( indVAR[2 * dim], indexVAR[2 * dim], i, iel );
1349  Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
1350  Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = ( *mysolution->_SolOld[indVAR[2 * dim]] ) ( idof );
1351  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] = 0.;
1352  }

1355  for ( int idim = 0; idim < 2 * dim; idim++ ) {
1356  dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[idim].begin(), dofsVAR[idim].end() );
1357  }
1358 
1359  dofsAll.insert ( dofsAll.end(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].begin(), dofsVAR[2 * dim].end() );
1360 
1361  //if (igrid==gridn || !myel->GetRefinedElementIndex(iel) ) {
1362 
1363  if (assembleMatrix) s.new_recording();
1364 
1365  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1366  for ( int j = 0; j < nve; j++ ) {
1367  vx[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][j];
1368  vx_old[idim][j] = vx_hat[idim][j] + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][j];
1369  }
1370  }
1371 
1372  // Boundary integral
1373  {
1374 
1375  vector < adept::adouble> normal ( dim, 0 );
1376  vector < double > normal_old ( dim, 0 );
1377 
1378  // loop on faces
1379  for ( unsigned jface = 0; jface < mymsh->GetElementFaceNumber ( iel ); jface++ ) {
1380  std::vector< double > xx ( dim, 0. );
1381 
1382  // look for boundary faces
1383  if ( myel->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) < 0 ) {
1384 
1385  unsigned int face = - ( mymsh->el->GetFaceElementIndex ( iel, jface ) + 1 );
1386  double tau = 0.;
1387  double tau_old = 0.;
1388  if ( ( !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "U", tau, face, time ) &&
1389  !ml_sol->GetBdcFunction() ( xx, "U", tau_old, face, time - dt ) )
1390  && ( tau != 0. || tau_old != 0. ) ) {
1391  //tau /= rhof;
1392  //tau_old /= rhof;
1393  unsigned nve = mymsh->GetElementFaceDofNumber ( iel, jface, SolType2 );
1394  const unsigned felt = mymsh->GetElementFaceType ( iel, jface );
1395 
1396  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
1397  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
1398  unsigned idof = mymsh->GetSolutionDof ( ilocal, iel, 2 );
1399 
1400  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1401  vx_face[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
1402  vx_face_old[idim][i] = ( *mymsh->_topology->_Sol[idim] ) ( idof ) + Soli_old[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal];
1403  }
1404  }
1405 
1406  for ( unsigned igs = 0; igs < mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); igs++ ) {
1407  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face, igs, Weight, phi, gradphi, normal );
1408  mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->JacobianSur ( vx_face_old, igs, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, normal_old );
1409 
1410  //phi1 =mymsh->_finiteElement[felt][SolType2]->GetPhi(igs);
1411  // *** phi_i loop ***
1412  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
1413  adept::adouble value = - phi[i] * tau / rhof * Weight;
1414  double value_old = - phi[i] * tau_old / rhof * Weight_old;
1415  unsigned int ilocal = mymsh->GetLocalFaceVertexIndex ( iel, jface, i );
1416 
1417  for ( unsigned idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1418  //if ( ( !solidmark[ilocal] ) ) {
1419  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][ilocal] += dt * ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
1420  //}
1421  //else { //if interface node it goes to solid
1422  // aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][ilocal] += dt * ( theta * value + ( 1. - theta ) * value_old ) * normal[idim];
1423  //}
1424  }
1425  }
1426  }
1427  }
1428  }
1429  }
1430  }
1431 
1432  // *** Gauss point loop ***
1433  double area = 1.;
1434 
1435  for ( unsigned ig = 0; ig < mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussPointNumber(); ig++ ) {
1436  // *** get Jacobian and test function and test function derivatives in the moving frame***
1437  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx, ig, Weight, phi, gradphi, nablaphi );
1438  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_hat, ig, Weight_hat, phi_hat, gradphi_hat, nablaphi_hat );
1439  mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->Jacobian ( vx_old, ig, Weight_old, phi_old, gradphi_old, nablaphi_old );
1440  phi1 = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType1]->GetPhi ( ig );
1441 
1442  if ( flag_mat == 2 || iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
1443  if ( ig == 0 ) {
1444  double GaussWeight = mymsh->_finiteElement[ielt][SolType2]->GetGaussWeight ( ig );
1445  area = Weight_hat / GaussWeight;
1446 
1447  if ( iel == mymsh->_elementOffset[iproc] ) {
1448  area_elem_first->add ( mymsh->processor_id(), area );
1449  area_elem_first->close();
1450  rapresentative_area = area_elem_first->l1_norm() / nprocs;
1451  }
1452  }
1453 
1454  Weight_nojac = Weight / area * rapresentative_area;
1455  }
1456 
1457  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1458  // displacement and velocity
1459  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
1460  SolVAR[i] = 0.;
1461  SolVAR_old[i] = 0.;
1462 
1463  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1464  GradSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1465  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1466 
1467  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1468  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1469  }
1470 
1471  for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
1472  NablaSolVAR[i][j] = 0.;
1473  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] = 0.;
1474  }
1475 
1476  for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve; inode++ ) {
1477  SolVAR[i] += phi[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1478  SolVAR_old[i] += phi_old[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1479 
1480  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1481  GradSolVAR[i][j] += gradphi[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1482  GradSolVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_old[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1483 
1484  GradSolhatVAR[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1485  GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] += gradphi_hat[inode * dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1486  }
1487  for ( int j = 0; j < nabla_dim; j++ ) {
1488  NablaSolVAR[i][j] += nablaphi[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1489  NablaSolVAR_old[i][j] += nablaphi_old[inode * nabla_dim + j] * Soli_old[indexVAR[i]][inode];
1490  }
1491  }
1492  }
1493 
1494  // pressure
1495  SolVAR[2 * dim] = 0.;
1496  SolVAR_old[2 * dim] = 0.;
1497 
1498  for ( unsigned inode = 0; inode < nve1; inode++ ) {
1499  SolVAR[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
1500  SolVAR_old[2 * dim] += phi1[inode] * Soli_old[indexVAR[2 * dim]][inode];
1501  }
1502 
1503  // Lagrangian mesh velocity at t = time + dt/2
1504  vector < adept::adouble > meshVel ( dim );
1505  vector < vector < adept::adouble > > GradMeshVel ( dim );
1506 
1507  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1508  meshVel[i] = ( SolVAR[i] - SolVAR_old[i] ) / dt;
1509  GradMeshVel[i].resize ( dim );
1510 
1511  for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1512  GradMeshVel[i][j] = ( GradSolVAR[i][j] - GradSolVAR_old[i][j] ) / dt;
1513  }
1514  }
1515 
1516  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1517  //BEGIN FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
1518  if ( flag_mat == 2 || flag_mat == 3 ) {
1519 
1520  vector < adept::adouble > a ( dim );
1521  vector < adept::adouble > a_old ( dim );
1522  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1523  a[i] = SolVAR[i + dim] - meshVel[i]; // maybe we subtract meshVel[i]
1524  a_old[i] = SolVAR_old[i + dim] - meshVel[i]; // maybe we subtract something??
1525  }
1526 
1527  // speed
1528  adept::adouble aL2Norm = 0.;
1529  adept::adouble a_oldL2Norm = 0.;
1530  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1531  aL2Norm += a[i] * a[i];
1532  a_oldL2Norm += a_old[i] * a_old[i];
1533  }
1534  aL2Norm = sqrt ( aL2Norm );
1535  a_oldL2Norm = sqrt ( a_oldL2Norm );
1536 
1537  double sqrtlambdak = ( *mysolution->_Sol[indLmbd] ) ( iel );
1538  adept::adouble tauSupg = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
1539  adept::adouble tauSupg_old = 1. / ( sqrtlambdak * sqrtlambdak * 4.*IRe );
1540  adept::adouble Rek = aL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
1541  adept::adouble Rek_old = a_oldL2Norm / ( 4.*sqrtlambdak * IRe );
1542 
1543  if ( Rek > 1.0e-15 ) {
1544  adept::adouble xiRek = ( Rek >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek;
1545  tauSupg = xiRek / ( aL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
1546  }
1547 
1548  if ( Rek_old > 1.0e-15 ) {
1549  adept::adouble xiRek_old = ( Rek_old >= 1. ) ? 1. : Rek_old;
1550  tauSupg_old = xiRek_old / ( a_oldL2Norm * sqrtlambdak );
1551  }
1552 
1553  //std::cout << tauSupg.value() <<" " <<tauSupg_old.value()<<std::endl;
1554 
1555 
1556  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg ( nve, 0. );
1557  vector < adept::adouble > phiSupg_old ( nve, 0. );
1558 // tauSupg=0;
1559 // tauSupg_old=0;
1560  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
1561  for ( unsigned j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1562  phiSupg[i] += ( ( SolVAR[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg;
1563  phiSupg_old[i] += ( ( SolVAR_old[j + dim] - meshVel[j] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + j] ) * tauSupg_old;
1564  }
1565  }
1566 
1567 
1568  //BEGIN ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1569  {
1570  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
1571 
1572  //BEGIN redidual Laplacian ALE map in the reference domain
1573  adept::adouble LapmapVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1574 
1575  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1576  for ( int jdim = 0; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
1577  LapmapVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1578  }
1579  }
1580 
1581  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1582  aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += ( !solidmark[i] ) * ( - LapmapVAR[idim] * Weight_nojac );
1583  }
1584 
1585  //END residual Laplacian ALE map in reference domain
1586 
1587  if ( flag_mat == 2 ) {
1588  //BEGIN residual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1589  adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1590  adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1591  adept::adouble LapStrong[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1592  adept::adouble LapStrong_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1593  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1594  adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1595 
1596  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1597  for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
1598  unsigned kdim;
1599  if ( idim == jdim ) kdim = jdim;
1600  else if ( 1 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim; // xy
1601  else if ( 2 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 2; // xz
1602  else if ( 3 == idim + jdim ) kdim = dim + 1; // yz
1603  //laplaciano debole
1604  LapvelVAR[idim] += ( GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1605  LapvelVAR_old[idim] += ( GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim] ) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1606  //laplaciano strong
1607  LapStrong[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg[i];
1608  LapStrong_old[idim] += ( NablaSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + NablaSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][kdim] ) * phiSupg_old[i];
1609 
1610  AdvaleVAR[idim] += ( ( SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1611  + ( GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1612  //) * phi[i];
1613  ) * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] );
1614 
1615  AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ( ( SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim] ) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1616  + ( GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim] ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1617  //) * phi_old[i];
1618  ) * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] );
1619  }
1620  }
1621 
1622  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1623 
1624  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( phi[i] + phiSupg[i] ) * Weight
1625  - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i] ) * Weight_old );
1626 
1627  adept::adouble value = theta * dt * (
1628  - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1629  - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1630  + IRe * LapStrong[idim]
1631  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1632  ) * Weight; // at time t
1633 
1634  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * dt * (
1635  - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1636  - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1637  + IRe * LapStrong_old[idim]
1638  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1639  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1640 
1641  //if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
1642  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1643  //}
1644  //else {
1645  // aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1646  // }
1647 
1648  }
1649  //END redidual Navier-Stokes in moving domain
1650  }
1651  else if ( flag_mat == 3 ) {
1652  //BEGIN redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1653 
1654 
1655  adept::adouble speed = 0.;
1656  adept::adouble speed_old = 0.;
1657  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1658  speed += SolVAR[dim + idim] * SolVAR[dim + idim];
1659  speed_old += SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * SolVAR_old[dim + idim];
1660  }
1661  double eps = 1.0e-12;
1662  speed = sqrt ( speed + eps );
1663  speed_old = sqrt ( speed_old + eps );
1664  double DE = 0.;
1665  if ( dim == 2 ) {
1666  DE = 0.00006; // turek2D
1667  }
1668  else if ( dim == 3 ) {
1669  DE = 0.000112; // porous3D
1670  }
1671  double b = 4188;
1672  double a = 1452;
1673  double K = DE * IRe * rhof / b; // alpha = mu/b * De
1674  double C2 = 2 * a / ( rhof * DE );
1675 
1676 
1677 
1678 
1679 
1680 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1681 // adept::adouble LapvelVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1682 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1683 // adept::adouble AdvaleVAR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1684 //
1685 // for(int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++) {
1686 // for(int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++) {
1687 //
1688 // LapvelVAR[idim] += (GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi[i * dim + jdim];
1689 // LapvelVAR_old[idim] += (GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim] + GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][idim]) * gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim];
1690 //
1691 // AdvaleVAR[idim] += ((SolVAR[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR[dim + idim][jdim]
1692 // + (GradSolVAR[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR[dim + idim]
1693 // ) * phi[i];
1694 //
1695 // AdvaleVAR_old[idim] += ((SolVAR_old[dim + jdim] - meshVel[jdim]) * GradSolVAR_old[dim + idim][jdim]
1696 // + (GradSolVAR_old[dim + jdim][jdim] - GradMeshVel[jdim][jdim]) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim]
1697 // ) * phi_old[i];
1698 // }
1699 // }
1700 
1701  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1702 
1703 // adept::adouble timeDerivative = -(SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
1704 // - SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old);
1705 
1706  adept::adouble value = theta * dt * (
1707 // - AdvaleVAR[idim] // advection term
1708 // - IRe * LapvelVAR[idim] // viscous dissipation
1709  //- SolVAR[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * phi[i]
1710  - (SolVAR[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi[i] + phiSupg[i])
1711  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1712  ) * Weight; // at time t
1713 
1714  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * dt * (
1715 // - AdvaleVAR_old[idim] // advection term
1716 // - IRe * LapvelVAR_old[idim] // viscous dissipation
1717  //- SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed_old ) * phi_old[i]
1718  - (SolVAR_old[dim + idim] - meshVel[idim]) * ( IRe / K + 0.5 * C2 * speed ) * (phi_old[i] + phiSupg_old[i])
1719  + SolVAR[2 * dim] * gradphi_old[i * dim + idim] // pressure gradient
1720  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1721 
1722  //if ( !solidmark[i] ) {
1723  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1724  //}
1725  //else {
1726  //aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += value + value_old;
1727  // }
1728 
1729  }
1730  //END redidual Porous Media in moving domain
1731  }
1732  }
1733  }
1734  //END ALE + Momentum (Navier-Stokes)
1735 
1736  //BEGIN continuity block
1737  {
1738  adept::adouble div_vel = 0.;
1739 
1740  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1741  div_vel += GradSolVAR[dim + i][i];
1742  }
1743 
1744  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
1745  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * div_vel ) * Weight;
1746  }
1747  }
1748  //END continuity block ===========================
1749  }
1750  //END FLUID ASSEMBLY ============
1751 
1752  //*******************************************************************************************************
1753 
1754  //BEGIN SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
1755  else {
1756  //BEGIN build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1757  //physical quantity
1758  adept::adouble J_hat;
1759  double J_hat_old;
1760  adept::adouble I_e;
1761  double I_e_old;
1762  adept::adouble Cauchy[3][3];
1763  adept::adouble Cauchy_old[3][3];
1764  double Id2th[3][3] = {{ 1., 0., 0.}, { 0., 1., 0.}, { 0., 0., 1.}};
1765 
1766 
1767 
1768 
1769  if ( solid_model == 0 ) { // Saint-Venant
1770  adept::adouble e[3][3];
1771  double e_old[3][3];
1772 
1773  //computation of the stress tensor
1774  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1775  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1776  e[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR[j][i] );
1777  e_old[i][j] = 0.5 * ( GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j] + GradSolhatVAR_old[j][i] );
1778  }
1779  }
1780 
1781  I_e = 0;
1782  I_e_old = 0;
1783 
1784  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1785  I_e += e[i][i];
1786  I_e_old += e_old[i][i];
1787  }
1788 
1789  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1790  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1791  //incompressible
1792  Cauchy[i][j] = 2 * mus * e[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1793  Cauchy_old[i][j] = 2 * mus * e_old[i][j] - 2 * mus * I_e_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[i][j];
1794  //+(penalty)*lambda*I_e*Id2th[i][j];
1795  }
1796  }
1797  }
1798 
1799  else { // hyperelastic non linear material
1800 
1801  adept::adouble I1_B = 0.;
1802  adept::adouble I2_B = 0.;
1803 
1804  double I1_B_old = 0.;
1805  double I2_B_old = 0.;
1806 
1807  adept::adouble F[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1808  adept::adouble B[3][3];
1809 
1810  double F_old[3][3] = {{1., 0., 0.}, {0., 1., 0.}, {0., 0., 1.}};
1811  double B_old[3][3];
1812 
1813  for ( int i = 0; i < dim; i++ ) {
1814  for ( int j = 0; j < dim; j++ ) {
1815  F[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR[i][j];
1816  F_old[i][j] += GradSolhatVAR_old[i][j];
1817  }
1818  }
1819 
1820  J_hat = F[0][0] * F[1][1] * F[2][2] + F[0][1] * F[1][2] * F[2][0] + F[0][2] * F[1][0] * F[2][1]
1821  - F[2][0] * F[1][1] * F[0][2] - F[2][1] * F[1][2] * F[0][0] - F[2][2] * F[1][0] * F[0][1];
1822 
1823  J_hat_old = F_old[0][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[2][2] + F_old[0][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[2][0]
1824  + F_old[0][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[2][1] - F_old[2][0] * F_old[1][1] * F_old[0][2]
1825  - F_old[2][1] * F_old[1][2] * F_old[0][0] - F_old[2][2] * F_old[1][0] * F_old[0][1];
1826 
1827 
1828  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
1829  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
1830  B[I][J] = 0.;
1831  B_old[I][J] = 0.;
1832 
1833  for ( int K = 0; K < 3; ++K ) {
1834  //left Cauchy-Green deformation tensor or Finger tensor (b = F*F^T)
1835  B[I][J] += F[I][K] * F[J][K];
1836  B_old[I][J] += F_old[I][K] * F_old[J][K];
1837  }
1838  }
1839  }
1840 
1841  if ( solid_model <= 4 ) { // Neo-Hookean
1842  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1843  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
1844 
1845  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
1846  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
1847  if ( 1 == solid_model ) { //Wood-Bonet J_hat =1;
1848  Cauchy[I][J] = mus * ( B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1849  Cauchy_old[I][J] = mus * ( B_old[I][J] - Id2th[I][J] ) - mus / 3.*I1_B_old * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1850  }
1851 
1852 // else if ( 2 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus/J_hat*B[I][J]
1853 // -mus/J_hat*SolVAR[2*dim]*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet J_hat !=1;
1854 // else if ( 3 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - Id2th[I][J])/J_hat
1855 // + lambda/J_hat*log(J_hat)*Id2th[I][J]; //Wood-Bonet penalty
1856 // else if ( 4 == solid_model ) Cauchy[I][J] = mus*(B[I][J] - I1_B*Id2th[I][J]/3.)/pow(J_hat,5./3.)
1857 // + lambda*(J_hat-1.)*Id2th[I][J]; //Allan-Bower
1858 //
1859  }
1860  }
1861  }
1862  else if ( 5 == solid_model ) { //Mooney-Rivlin
1863  adept::adouble detB = B[0][0] * ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[2][1] * B[1][2] )
1864  - B[0][1] * ( B[2][2] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] )
1865  + B[0][2] * ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] );
1866 
1867  double detB_old = B_old[0][0] * ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[2][1] * B_old[1][2] )
1868  - B_old[0][1] * ( B_old[2][2] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] )
1869  + B_old[0][2] * ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] );
1870 
1871  adept::adouble invdetB = 1. / detB;
1872  double invdetB_old = 1. / detB_old;
1873  adept::adouble invB[3][3];
1874  double invB_old[3][3];
1875 
1876  invB[0][0] = ( B[1][1] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
1877  invB[1][0] = - ( B[0][1] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][1] ) * invdetB;
1878  invB[2][0] = ( B[0][1] * B[1][2] - B[0][2] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
1879  invB[0][1] = - ( B[1][0] * B[2][2] - B[1][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
1880  invB[1][1] = ( B[0][0] * B[2][2] - B[0][2] * B[2][0] ) * invdetB;
1881  invB[2][1] = - ( B[0][0] * B[1][2] - B[1][0] * B[0][2] ) * invdetB;
1882  invB[0][2] = ( B[1][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[1][1] ) * invdetB;
1883  invB[1][2] = - ( B[0][0] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
1884  invB[2][2] = ( B[0][0] * B[1][1] - B[1][0] * B[0][1] ) * invdetB;
1885 
1886  invB_old[0][0] = ( B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1887  invB_old[1][0] = - ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1888  invB_old[2][0] = ( B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1889  invB_old[0][1] = - ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
1890  invB_old[1][1] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][2] - B_old[0][2] * B_old[2][0] ) * invdetB_old;
1891  invB_old[2][1] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][2] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][2] ) * invdetB_old;
1892  invB_old[0][2] = ( B_old[1][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[1][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1893  invB_old[1][2] = - ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1894  invB_old[2][2] = ( B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] - B_old[1][0] * B_old[0][1] ) * invdetB_old;
1895 
1896 
1897  I1_B = B[0][0] + B[1][1] + B[2][2];
1898  I2_B = B[0][0] * B[1][1] + B[1][1] * B[2][2] + B[2][2] * B[0][0]
1899  - B[0][1] * B[1][0] - B[1][2] * B[2][1] - B[2][0] * B[0][2];
1900 
1901  I1_B_old = B_old[0][0] + B_old[1][1] + B_old[2][2];
1902  I2_B_old = B_old[0][0] * B_old[1][1] + B_old[1][1] * B_old[2][2] + B_old[2][2] * B_old[0][0]
1903  - B_old[0][1] * B_old[1][0] - B_old[1][2] * B_old[2][1] - B_old[2][0] * B_old[0][2];
1904 
1905  //double C1 = mus / 3.;
1906  double C1 = ( elementGroup == 15 ) ? mus1 / 3. : mus / 3.;
1907  double C2 = C1 / 2.;
1908 
1909  for ( int I = 0; I < 3; ++I ) {
1910  for ( int J = 0; J < 3; ++J ) {
1911  Cauchy[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B[I][J] - C2 * invB[I][J] )
1912  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B - C2 * I2_B) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1913  - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1914 
1915  Cauchy_old[I][J] = 2.* ( C1 * B_old[I][J] - C2 * invB_old[I][J] )
1916  //- (2. / 3.) * (C1 * I1_B_old - C2 * I2_B_old) * SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1917  - SolVAR[2 * dim] * Id2th[I][J];
1918 
1919  }
1920  }
1921 
1922  }
1923  }
1924 
1925  //END build Chauchy Stress in moving domain
1926 
1927  //BEGIN v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1928  {
1929  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve; i++ ) {
1930 
1931  //BEGIN redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
1932  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1933  aRhs[indexVAR[0 * dim + idim]][i] += - phi[i] * ( -SolVAR[idim] + SolVAR_old[idim] +
1934  dt * ( theta * SolVAR[dim + idim] + ( 1. - theta ) * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] )
1935  ) * Weight_hat;
1936  }
1937 
1938  //END redidual d_t - v = 0 in fixed domain
1939 
1940  //BEGIN redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1941  adept::adouble CauchyDIR[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1942  adept::adouble CauchyDIR_old[3] = {0., 0., 0.};
1943 
1944  for ( int idim = 0.; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1945  for ( int jdim = 0.; jdim < dim; jdim++ ) {
1946  CauchyDIR[idim] += gradphi[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy[idim][jdim];
1947  CauchyDIR_old[idim] += gradphi_old[i * dim + jdim] * Cauchy_old[idim][jdim];
1948  }
1949  }
1950 
1951  for ( int idim = 0; idim < dim; idim++ ) {
1952 
1953  adept::adouble timeDerivative = - ( rhos * SolVAR[dim + idim] * phi[i] * Weight
1954  - rhos * SolVAR_old[dim + idim] * phi_old[i] * Weight_old );
1955 
1956  adept::adouble value = theta * dt * ( rhos * phi[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
1957  - CauchyDIR[idim] // stress
1958  ) * Weight; // at time t
1959 
1960  adept::adouble value_old = ( 1. - theta ) * dt * ( rhos * phi_old[i] * _gravity[idim] // body force
1961  - CauchyDIR_old[idim] // stress
1962  ) * Weight_old; // at time t-dt
1963 
1964  //aRhs[indexVAR[idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1965  aRhs[indexVAR[dim + idim]][i] += timeDerivative + value + value_old;
1966  }
1967 
1968  //END redidual Solid Momentum in moving domain
1969  }
1970  }
1971  //END v=0 + Momentum (Solid)
1972 
1973  //BEGIN continuity block
1974  {
1975  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < nve1; i++ ) {
1976  if ( !penalty ) {
1977  if ( 0 == solid_model ) {
1978  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += - ( -phi1[i] * ( I_e + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) ) * Weight_hat;
1979  }
1980  else if ( 1 == solid_model || 5 == solid_model ) {
1981  aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][i] += phi1[i] * ( J_hat - 1. + ( !incompressible ) / lambda * SolVAR[2 * dim] ) * Weight_hat;
1982  }
1983 
1984 // else if (2 == solid_model){
1985 // aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( log(J_hat)/J_hat + (!incompressible)/lambda*SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
1986 // }
1987  }
1988 
1989 // else if (3 == solid_model || 4 == solid_model){ // pressure = 0 in the solid
1990 // aRhs[indexVAR[2*dim]][i] += -(-phi1[i]*( SolVAR[2*dim] ) )*Weight_hat;
1991 // }
1992  }
1993  }
1994  //END continuity block
1995  }
1996 
1997  //END SOLID ASSEMBLY ============
1998  }
1999 
2000  //}
2001 
2002  //BEGIN local to global assembly
2003  //copy adouble aRhs into double Rhs
2004  for ( unsigned i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
2005  for ( int j = 0; j < nve; j++ ) {
2006  Rhs[indexVAR[i]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[i]][j].value();
2007  }
2008  }
2009 
2010  for ( unsigned j = 0; j < nve1; j++ ) {
2011  Rhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j] = aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][j].value();
2012  }
2013 
2014  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim + 1; i++ ) {
2015  myRES->add_vector_blocked ( Rhs[indexVAR[i]], dofsVAR[i] );
2016  }
2017 
2018  if (assembleMatrix) {
2019  //Store equations
2020  for ( int i = 0; i < 2 * dim; i++ ) {
2021  s.dependent ( &aRhs[indexVAR[i]][0], nve );
2022  s.independent ( &Soli[indexVAR[i]][0], nve );
2023  }
2024 
2025  s.dependent ( &aRhs[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1 );
2026  s.independent ( &Soli[indexVAR[2 * dim]][0], nve1 );
2027  s.jacobian ( &Jac[0] );
2028  unsigned nveAll = ( 2 * dim * nve + nve1 );

1565  std::cout << "The 3D matrix is not symmetric" << std::endl;
1566  }
1567 
1568  std::vector < std::vector <double> > B (2);
1569  for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
1570  B[i].resize (2);
1571  }
1572 
1573  B[0][0] = A[0][0];
1574  B[0][1] = A[0][1];
1575  B[1][0] = A[1][0];
1576  B[1][1] = A[1][1];

1578 
1579

1581  SPD = false;
1582  }
1583 
1584  else {
1585  double l00 = sqrt (A[0][0]);
1586  double l11 = sqrt (A[1][1] - ( (A[0][1] * A[0][1]) / A[0][0]));

1588 
1589  double detL = l00 * l11;

1591  for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
1592  Lm1[i].resize (2);
1593  }
1594 
1595  Lm1[0][0] = (1 / detL) * l11;
1596  Lm1[1][0] = - (1 / detL) * l01;
1597  Lm1[0][1] = 0. ;
1598  Lm1[1][1] = (1 / detL) * l00 ;
1599 
1600  std::vector < double > K (2);
1601 
1602  K[0] = Lm1[0][0] * A[0][2] + Lm1[0][1] * A[1][2];
1603  K[1] = Lm1[1][0] * A[0][2] + Lm1[1][1] * A[1][2];
1604 
1605  double KK = sqrt (K[0] * K[0] + K[1] * K[1]) ;
1606 
1607  if (A[2][2] - KK < 0 || fabs (A[2][2] - KK) < 1.0e-8) {
1608  SPD = false;
1609  }
1610  }
1611 
1612  if (SPD == true) {
1613  std::cout << "The 3D matrix is SPD" << std::endl;
1614  }
1615 
1616  else {
1617  std::cout << "The 3D matrix is not SPD" << std::endl;
1618  }
1619 
1620  return SPD;
1621 
1622  }
